headline: Siemens unveils lineup for CES 2026 keynote
summary: MUNICH, December 17, 2025--Siemens today announced the lineup of industry and technology leaders who will join President and CEO Roland Busch on stage for Siemens’ keynote at CES 2026.

headline: The Market Isn't Broken - It's Rotating, And I'm Positioning For What's Next
summary: US public equity universe halved since 1990s, with many top opportunities now in private markets. Read why Main Street could be in a terrific spot for the years ahead.
